  "description": "A highly customized plugin to bring bounty's to PMMP (only pmmp, no forks/spoons)",
  "readme_markdown": "<a href=\"https://tiny.cc/JaxksDC\"><img src=\"https://discordapp.com/api/guilds/554059221847638040/embed.png\" alt=\"Discord server\"/></a> <a href=\"https://poggit.pmmp.io/p/Bounty\"><img src=\"https://poggit.pmmp.io/shield.state/Bounty\"></a> <a href=\"https://poggit.pmmp.io/p/Bounty\"><img src=\"https://poggit.pmmp.io/shield.dl.total/Bounty\"></a>\n\n# Bounty\n\nA highly customized plugin to bring bounty's to PMMP (only pmmp, no forks/spoons)\nMade by Jaxk (aka Jackthehack), thank you to the community in the above discord for providing soo many suggestions !\n\n### Usage:\n- /bounty help/ver/credits\n- /bounty new/add name amount\n- /bounty list page\n\n### Events:\nOnly bother looking here if you know what your doing :)\n\nAll events are cancellable and extend BountyEvent.\n- BountyAddEvent\n- BountyClaimEvent\n- BountyCreateEvent\n- BountyRemoveEvent\n\n### API:\nAPI Functions:\n- Main::getInstance()\n- Main->hasBounty(string $name): bool\n- Main->getBounty(string $nick): int\n- *More coming soon.*",
